      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in breathtaking mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the factory floor. With a flawless exterior and a pristine interior that still feels brand new, this is a rare find for any discerning driver looking for perfection.",
